Difficulties in Emoption Regulation Scale - 16 (Bjureberg et al. 2016

Scoring: 	1: Almost Never 
	        2: Sometimes 
	        3: About half the time 
	        4: Most of the time 
	        5: Almost always 
          
Item      
DERS1     	I have difficulty making sense out of my feelings
DERS2       I am confused about how I feel
DERS3     	When I’m upset, I have difficulty getting work done
DERS4	      When I’m upset, I become out of control
DERS5	      When I’m upset, I believe I will remain that way for a long time
DERS6	      When I’m upset, I believe that I’ll end up feeling very depressed
DERS7	      When I’m upset, I have difficulty focusing on other things
DERS8	      When I’m upset, I feel ashamed with myself for feeling that way
DERS9	      When I am upset, I feel out of control
DERS10	    When I’m upset, I feel like I am weak
DERS11	    When I’m upset, I have difficulty controlling my behaviours
DERS12	    When I’m upset, I believe there is nothing I can do to make myself feel better
DERS13	    When I’m upset, I become irritated with myself for feeling that way
DERS14	    When I’m upset, I start to feel very bad about myself
DERS15	    When I’m upset, I have difficulty thinking about anything else
DERS16	    When I’m upset, my emotions feel overwhelming

R CODE 
mydata$DERS <- (mydata$DERS1 + mydata$DERS2 + mydata$DERS3 + mydata$DERS4 + mydata$DERS5 + mydata$DERS6 + mydata$DERS7 + mydata$DERS8 + mydata$DERS9 + mydata$DERS10 + mydata$DERS11 + mydata$DERS12 + mydata$DERS13 + mydata$DERS14 + mydata$DERS15 + mydata$DERS16)
